          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Targets of natural mercury oxide pellets with thickness",
                "of 815 and 509-mg/cm**2 were irradiated with incident",
                "proton beam energy, using a steel target holder with",
                "back water cooling.",
                "For the thin target irradiation HgO-445-mg/cm**2,",
                "a target holder made of aluminum was  O1264  3    9",
                "fabricated and it was water-cooled in the front and in",
                "the back of the target.",
                "The incident beam energy on the target was reduced to",
                "19-MeV due to the water layer and the target windows."
              ]
            }
